title: Mr Boukadoum discusses with his Bosnian counterpart ways to strengthen bilateral cooperation
text: Foreign Minister, Mr Sabri Boukadoum, made a phone call on Thursday with Bosnia and Herzegovina's Foreign Minister, Mrs Bisera Turkovic.

The two sides discussed the prospects of strengthening cooperation between the Algeria and Bosnia and Herzegovina, and the forthcoming opening of an embassy of his country in Algeria, in addition to a series of international and regional issues, including the latest developments in the region of Balkans.
